ially roll out <a href="https://developer.paypal.com/docs/classic/adaptive-payments/integration-guide/APIntro/" target="_blank">PayPal Adaptive Payments</a>  the most globally accepted escrow gateway option. Next in line will be an up-and-coming escrow service called, <a href="https://www.balancedpayments.com/" target="_blank">Balanced Payments</a>. Both are powerful solutions that any site owner should consider to maximize their sales.<br />\n<span id="more-8543"></span></p>\n<h3>Pricing</h3>\n<p>- PayPal Adaptive Payments &#8211; <strong><em>FREE</em></strong><br />\n- Balanced Payments &#8211; available as an add-on plugin in our <a href="http://marketplace.appthemes.com">WordPress Marketplace</a>.</p>\n<p>The base code will be added to our <a href="http://docs.appthemes.com/dev/payments/">payments module</a> later this month and bundled with each upcoming theme release. Look for it to hit the shelves in HireBee 1.2 and Taskerr 1.1 (both due out in mid Sept).</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=LNbsLVzgx9o:yIZ4wemS8-E:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=LNbsLVzgx9o:yIZ4wemS8-E:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=LNbsLVzgx9o:yIZ4wemS8-E:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=LNbsLVzgx9o:yIZ4wemS8-E:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=LNbsLVzgx9o:yIZ4wemS8-E:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=LNbsLVzgx9o:yIZ4wemS8-E:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?a=LNbsLVzgx9o:yIZ4wemS8-E:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/appthemes?i=LNbsLVzgx9o:yIZ4wemS8-E:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://fe